{
 "name": "RPlog_Morganna_Reveals_A_Source",
 "title": "Morganna Reveals a Source",
 "summary": "In the marble conference chamber of the Imperial Embassy, the imposing Imperial Joir, surrounded by datapads bearing Sienar Fleet Systems and Bureau of Operations crests, meets with the scarred Ambassador Morganna. Over wine and water, Morganna probes Joir about Sienar's commercial intentions in the Caspar sector, framing the discussion as protecting her corner of space. The two cold, calculating Imperials feel each other out in a careful exchange of business interests and intelligence, the cathedral-like chamber underscoring the weight of the pacts being made.",
